Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Tile>

    public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Tile>
    This class is used by Graph.java in order to make A* pathfinding easier. A "tile" is a bird's eye view square of the map.
